data.name: Escape of the Unchained
data.desc: Target 1 "Unchained" monster you control and 1 card on the field; destroy both. If this Set card is destroyed by card effect: You can Special Summon 1 "Unchained" monster from your Deck. You can only use each effect of "Escape of the Unchained" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
